---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import HomeHero from '../components/HomeHero.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Home">
  <HomeHero />

  <section class="content-card">
    <h2>About Me</h2>
    <p>
      I am a member of technical staff at AMD in Austin, where I work on formal verification of
      microprocessor designs. My work focuses on scalable verification flows, model checking, and tooling
      for industrial hardware verification.
    </p>
    <p>
      Before AMD, I was a research and development engineer at IBM, where I worked on formal hardware
      verification algorithms and tools.
    </p>
    <p>
      I received my PhD in Computer Science from Iowa State University, where I worked in the
      <a href="http://laboratory.temporallogic.org/">Laboratory for Temporal Logic</a> and was advised by
      <a href="https://www.aere.iastate.edu/kyrozier/">Kristin Y. Rozier</a> and
      <a href="http://web.cs.iastate.edu/~ciardo/">Gianfranco Ciardo</a>. I also earned an M.S. in Embedded
      Systems from the University of Pennsylvania and a B.E. from the University of Delhi.
    </p>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
